{
  "stem": "19690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 64.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then the seven of us lived together until we left Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The main focus then was twofold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Number one, my uncle and my father went to Mannheim every day to learn to become barbers because they felt they needed a trade if they went to another country and this was a trade that they could easily learn.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The other thing was get papers to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "By now, it was 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We finally got papers in the beginning of '39.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We went to Stuttgart and got-- had our examinations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the visa was issued in April of '39 and it was good for three months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we tried desperately-- no, four months, it was good for four months-- and we tried to get out desperately, but transportation was not to be had, number one.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It had to be paid for from outside Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We couldn't pay for our own transportation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All the ships were full because everybody was trying to get out desperately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My Uncle Julius, who was the driver originally, when he came back, he had papers waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he-- but they were only visitor's-- visitor's permit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he left immediately after he came home, went to the United States, sat in front of one of my grandmother's brother's offices for two months until the man would give him a visa-- an affidavit, rather-- went back to Germany, got his visa, and they got out in August of 1939, just before the war started.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They left through Amsterdam just before the war started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So they got out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We tried through Italy to Genoa, through Portugal, through Holland and Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We couldn't get passage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And finally, the war had already been declared.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
